<DocsLayout title="Manage Lists" section="Company Setup">
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Customize the drop-down lists used throughout Field Promax to organize and manage work orders effectively.
    Configure job types, priorities, marketing campaigns, and other categories to match your business needs.
  </p>
  <p>
    Well-organized drop-down lists help you group work orders by category, streamline dispatching,
    filter efficiently, and track performance across campaigns.
  </p>

  <h2>How to Access</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>From the left panel, go to <strong>Settings</strong> â†’ <strong>Manage Lists</strong></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Available Lists</h2>
  <img src="/images/company-setup/managelists_01.jpg" alt="Manage Lists Screen" />

  <h3>Job Type</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Classify work orders by type (e.g., "Heating," "Plumbing," "Residential," "Commercial")</li>
    <li>Group and filter work orders by Job Type</li>
    <li>Job Types are visible on your calendar for quick reference</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Priority</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Define priority levels such as High, Medium, or Low</li>
    <li>Helps dispatchers identify urgent jobs quickly</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Secondary Status</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Technicians can update secondary status via the mobile app</li>
    <li>Examples: "Customer Not Available," "Waiting on Parts"</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Vehicles</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Maintain a list of company vehicles</li>
    <li>Track miles driven for each vehicle</li>
    <li>Run reports for total miles by month</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Work Groups</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Organize technicians into groups</li>
    <li>Filter calendar views by work group</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Marketing Campaign</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Track where customers find your services</li>
    <li>Run monthly reports to measure campaign effectiveness</li>
    <li>Customize the field name to suit your business</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Custom Pricing</h3>
  <p>
    Set customer-specific pricing for products. See the <a href="/auxiliary-modules/custom-pricing">Custom Pricing</a> tutorial for details.
  </p>

  <h3>Equipment Tracking</h3>
  <p>
    Track equipment and maintenance history. See the <a href="/auxiliary-modules/equipment-tracking">Equipment Tracking</a> tutorial for details.
  </p>

  <h3>Checklists</h3>
  <p>
    Create task checklists for quality control. See the <a href="/auxiliary-modules/checklist">Checklist</a> tutorial for details.
  </p>

  <h2>User Permissions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Only <strong>Administrators</strong> can modify lists and customize settings</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Tips</h2>
  <div class="callout callout-tip">
    <p>
      <strong>Use grouping</strong> to quickly find work orders by Job Type or Secondary Status.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Customize your lists</strong> to match your specific workflows and maximize the benefits of Field Promax.
    </p>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
